You heard him, right? My husband
is a stubborn one all right...

rows.label: qst000508_msg0002
rows.name:
With my help, they might be able to
convince him, but it's all for nothing
if they're not here...

rows.label: qst000508_msg0003

Sometimes I think, if Riana is happy
with her life like this, maybe that is
for the best...

rows.label: qst000508_msg0004
rows.name: I don't know what to do...
